<p style="text-align: left;"><a class="extLink" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1imAk_AVTSZo3qUCI4nO3KIcIojmIuOFze5cKNZ4gd2I/edit" title="Sign Up - 48 Hour Film Festival" target="_blank">Sign up HERE!</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">REQUIREMENTS FOR FILMS:</p>
<ul>
<li>Maximum submission length not to exceed 5 minutes but must be at least 2 minutes.</li>
<li>Theme and other instructions will be given at the pre-festival meeting on March 13 at 6 p.m. in the M.C. Theater.</li>
<li>No graphic violence: gratuitous blood or fighting, content designed to shock or un-nerve.&nbsp;</li>
<li>No graphic death scenes. Death must take place off camera, but can be implied through editing. Use your best judgement. Talent Activities reserves the right to make final judgement on appropriateness.</li>
<li>No sexually explicit content or innuendos.</li>
<li>Must be Honor Code and Dress Code appropriate, absolutely no cross-gender dressing.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Appropriate music:&nbsp; no vulgar language or lyrics or inappropriate references to deity.</li>
</ul>]]></AdditionalInformation></xPower><EventImage type="imagefile" label="Event Image" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true" Width="368" Height="672" Alignment="" Border="" Expanded="true" AlternateText="" HSpace="" VSpace="">activities/talent/DSC-(18)cr.jpg</EventImage><xPower Type="List" List="Images" Name="Images" label="Gallery Images" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Width="" Border="" Alignment="" Expanded="false" Height=""><Images type="imagefile" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Width="2200" Border="" Alignment="" Expanded="true" Height="3300" AlternateText="" HSpace="" VSpace=""></Images></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x6793" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x6784" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl" Expanded="false"/></EventsDetail>
